Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.59,1:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,twist your ankle and by surrendering to\Nit within minutes get up and walk away
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.24,1:01:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,like nothing happened.\NYou don't call it a twisted ankle. You
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.31,1:01:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,don't call it pain.\NThere's a nonverbal experiencing of
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.92,1:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever is flowing in towards you and\Nyou let go resisting it completely and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.20,1:01:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,become one with it. As you do that, the\Npain leaves your ankle and it becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.20,1:01:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,diffused. You could feel the pain in\Nyour whole aura and you completely and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.88,1:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,totally surrender to it and you can't\Ncall it pain. If you call it pain,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.96,1:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to suffer.\NYou call it nothing at all. You just
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.20,1:01:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to the presence of whatever\Nthat is. And within minutes it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.40,1:01:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears and you get up and you walk\Naway.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.07,1:02:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how you take off weight.\NYou don't call yourself you can't call
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.04,1:02:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it hunger. That's labeling it and giving\Nit power that it doesn't have. Instead,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.04,1:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,there's this sensation. What you do is\Nyou lay down and you let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.24,1:02:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the sensation just like you do with the\Ntwisted ankle. Don't call it hunger.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.59,1:02:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whole that's a program.\NYou lay down and you let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.52,1:02:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this sensation. You let go resisting the\Nsensation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.40,1:02:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden it becomes diffuse. It's\Nnot in your stomach at all. It's
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.76,1:02:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere in your aura.\NYou lay down and you let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.16,1:02:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,this sensation.\NAfter about five or minutes or so, it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.96,1:02:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears.\NThen you get up and walk away from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.24,1:02:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you eat or not is immaterial. At\Nthat point, you can eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.64,1:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The other trick to pull on it is never\Nallow yourself to get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.07,1:02:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anticipate. What time do you always get\Nhungry? You get hungry dinner. Dinner
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.31,1:03:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,time 6:00, right? 4:30 you when you're\Nnot hungry, you have a piece of cheese
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.04,1:03:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and some crackers.\N5:00 you have half a banana. When dinner
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.35,1:03:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,comes around, you're not even going to\Nbe hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.24,1:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That you just snacked when you weren't\Nhungry. Right? So I call that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.00,1:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,prophylactic eating. So there's\Nprophylactic eating and letting go,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.07,1:03:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,resisting it until you've unconditioned\Nyourself to Pavlov's bell. You see, if
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.83,1:03:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a sensation and you label that\Nhunger,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.00,1:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,then you feed it. Now you just reinforce\Nthe Pavlovian conditioning. So every
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.79,1:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,time you eat when you're hungry, you\Nreinforce the Pavlovian conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.44,1:03:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, you can't get off of it.\NNow you're at the effect of hunger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.31,1:03:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at the effect of the belief in\Nhunger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.72,1:03:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The wor the best that you can do is\Nresist it and suffer and feel miserable,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.72,1:03:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're not going to lose weight.\NYou took off a few pounds, but I'll tell
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.35,1:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you in a year it'll be back. So, because\Nyou haven't changed the conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.68,1:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's simple. Never eat when you're\Nhungry. Anticipate in advance when
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.92,1:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be hungry. Have\Nsomething now when you're not hungry. If
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.96,1:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not hungry, half a hamburger will\Nbe quite satisfying because you're not
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.40,1:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,hungry in the first place. Eat two hot\Ndogs, one half of a lollipop, and you'll
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.55,1:04:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,be satisfied.\NNow, I admitted our daily menu, didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.96,1:04:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I?\NThat's how you decondition yourself to
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.96,1:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. So, those are, see, the Buddha\Nsaid, uh, through sense we become
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.35,1:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,attached. And the Buddha emphasized the\Nimportance of detachment.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.59,1:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To detach means to decondition yourself\Nmeans to perceive of it, to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.11,1:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,what's happening from a different way.\NSo I'm trying to explain a different
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.35,1:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,way. Never label it. Never call it\Nanything. Never resist it. And it loses
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.72,1:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,its power over you. In that way, you can\Ngo to the dentist and feel no pain. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.72,1:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They can take off your they could do an\Northopedic amputation and you experience
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.76,1:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,no pain at all. But the instant you\Nresist it or call it pain, then it's
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.11,1:05:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,very severe.\NAs they munch on the bone, you can
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.11,1:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,shrink right through the ceiling. That\Ncomes from resisting it. So,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.52,1:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and when we get to\Nmeditative techniques, we'll talk more
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.48,1:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,about\Nthe now of riding the crest of the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.35,1:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.\NThe minute you label a thing anticipated
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.20,1:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or resisted, you're off the crest of the\Nmoment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.20,1:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay in the exact moment of now\Nmeans you cannot resist anything
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.59,1:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,whatsoever.\NThen
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.28,1:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're in a very high space and you can\Ntranscend vertically in an instant into
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.68,1:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a great space. Then you're beyond\Nsuffering. To suffer is to resist the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.20,1:06:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,wave. Huh? Pain is one thing. Suffering\Nis another. They're not the same thing
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.83,1:06:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at all. You have to recondition your\Nmind. Pain is one thing. Suffering is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.48,1:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,something else.\NIt's possible to experience incredible
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.48,1:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,pain without any suffering. And it's\Npossible to suffer a great deal without
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.35,1:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,actually being in pain.\NSo you dissociate the two things.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.96,1:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffering is the resistance of that\Nwhich is painful. But when you let go
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.96,1:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,resisting pain, it loses its capacity to\Ncause you to suffer. Anybody who's ever
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.55,1:06:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,had narcotics knows that.\NIf you ever got had a gallbladder attack
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.07,1:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and they give you a shot of opium, it's\Nincredible. The pain is still there, but
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.72,1:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't bother you in the slightest.\NYou don't even care if it's there
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.00,1:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's not you. You're not\Nsuffering from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.68,1:06:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a delightful and miraculous\Nstate. And you can see why opium was
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.07,1:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,called many years ago or morphine was\Ncalled God's own medicine because it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.64,1:07:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,took you out of the suffering.\NUh but the pain still was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.35,1:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so it's a dissociating. So pain is\None thing. Suffering is another and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.03,1:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,letting go, resisting things is the way\Nout of the pain of anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.31,1:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more questions and then we'll stop\Nand we'll talk to anybody who wants to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.52,1:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,talk. And\N>> oh, I just love
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.52,1:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> slay everybody.\N>> And I want to hear how Mother Teresa and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.96,1:07:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorbachev came to endorse your book.\N>> Mother Teresa,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.35,1:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Teresa calibrates at 700. She has\Nenormous heart
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.00,1:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I experienced the truth of her when\NI was uh I went into incredible state
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.00,1:07:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and after that I couldn't practice for\Nsome time but I then I slowly went back
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.31,1:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,after some period of time um and what\Nactually happened was very severe cases
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.28,1:07:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,came from all over the world I\Neventually ended up with the biggest
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.88,1:08:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,psychiatric practice in the United\NStates actually 2,000 outpatient
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.20,1:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,patients, a thousand new patients a\Nyear. I had 50 employees, 26 offices and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.16,1:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,laboratories, research laboratories,\Netc.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.52,1:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a huge hospital practice as\Nwell. And into the hospital came the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.71,1:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,worst possible cases,\Ngiven up by everybody, hopeless, and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.44,1:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,some incredible just to witness them.\NThey'd be wound up in wet sheets brought
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.60,1:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in in a\Nmanacles uh from Maryland or someplace
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.79,1:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and this uh writhing body would be put\Non the floor
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.75,1:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there was instantly seeing\Nthrough the eyes seeing the self seeing
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.15,1:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the self of the entity within this\Npsychotic mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.75,1:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly there was like a healingness.\NThe healingness was of the spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.64,1:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,within.\NAnd at that point the entity within
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.08,1:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't have cared less about\Nuh the state of the mind body. It like
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.15,1:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,realized its own truth. And in that\Ninstant there was a healing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.00,1:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,uh which was what Mother Teresa did. She\Nlooked into the soul
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.44,1:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ugly dying\Nof
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.75,1:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what was it they died of in those years?\N>> Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.88,1:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Leopards.\N>> Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.64,1:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what went on.\NI have permission to ask that. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.48,1:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is yes. Resist. Yes.\NPrecisely the same phenomena. So
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.56,1:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore, I understood her heart. Um\Nand so when I wrote her, you know, she
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.08,1:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote me back and uh and uh there was\Nlike an awareness of the level out of
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.19,1:10:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which uh\Nher heart was
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.32,1:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,uh coming. There was like a mut\Nawareness of heart there. She understood
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.56,1:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,heart. You know, in the lecture I'm\Ngiving today, I should probably be bored
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.80,1:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with it.\NWhy do you talk about such things?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.56,1:10:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're not necessary. Huh? Because\Nif you can come through a heart that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.88,1:10:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 700, of course, who needs\Nit? But that's a different lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.44,1:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about the heart today.\NI don't want anybody loving anybody to
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.64,1:10:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lecture on heart.\NWe have to build to that. It's a because
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.96,1:10:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the most difficult of all. It's\Nvery hard to deliver such a
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.71,1:10:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,discussion because it begins to come up\Nand overwhelm
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.44,1:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you and it's difficult to talk. So\Nany more questions and then we'll
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.92,1:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,meet with anybody that wants to say\Nhello etc. Huh? Or is that sufficient?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.44,1:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N>> I'm confused about if if my body is a
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.32,1:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,result of karma running itself then how\Nam I still to have the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.19,1:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences within this body to\Ndisidentify
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.36,1:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> well because I mean you're not the body\Nhuh so the condition of the body or
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.88,1:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you identify with the body is\Nreally irrelevant to your spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.88,1:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution\Nwe would say that karmically you've
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.12,1:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,inherited the necessity\Nby having a physical body to overcome
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.71,1:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,those residuals from\Nuh the body's evolution uh through the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.80,1:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,animal kingdom.\NEverybody here has to learn how to
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.56,1:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,handle hunger, anger, fear, loss,\Ndefense, aggression because everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.15,1:12:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,here has a physical body and for it to\Nsurvive certain things then will tend to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.52,1:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,persist.\NSo there is a certain necessity then
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.04,1:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that befalls anyone who has a human body\Njust emanating from their bodiness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.48,1:12:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,itself. Right?\NAnd to correct all those propensities is
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.52,1:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what we talked about this morning\Nbecause they translate into the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.04,1:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,positionalities of the ego and as you\Nlet them go the identification with the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.12,1:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,body disappears. When that does, whether\Nit survives or not is really immaterial.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.60,1:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it dies or whether it gets blown\Nup is immaterial. I remember because I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.08,1:12:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,had that experience at age 12 in the\NNavy. Your mind sweepers are blowing up
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.48,1:12:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and falling and going going down in the\Ntornadoes or not the tornadoes whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.92,1:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they typhoon etc. And there wasn't the\Nslightest fear of anything at all. Just
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.71,1:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there was uh I in fact I was in a joyful\Nstate all the time high as hell. And uh
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.00,1:13:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you know if you died great I mean there\Nwas no identification with the body. So
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.19,1:13:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the the bodiness does not hold you back.\NIt's only your identification with the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.19,1:13:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,bodiness. Just as in it isn't the ego\Nthat's holding you back. It's your
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.80,1:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with the ego. So you\Ndon't have to un undo or destroy the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.67,1:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ego. You just have to stop identifying\Nwith it as who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.00,1:13:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So, we'll stop here and I thank\Nyou all and anybody wants to say hello,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.36,1:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be glad to\Ntell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.80,1:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Are you going to calibrate the audience?\N>> Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.00,1:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Great. What was 8? 130.\N>> Calgiate. We have permission to
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.23,1:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate the audience. We just There\Nwere 435, 437, 438, 439, 440, 441. Oh my
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.67,1:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,god, they went up 10 points. Yeah. Let's\Nsee. Let's make sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.60,1:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> No, it was 20, wasn't it?\N>> They went up was 340. They went
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.12,1:14:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> what?\N>> They went up 10 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.44,1:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> 432.\N>> 431. They went up to 440. 441.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.92,1:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It went from 431 to 440. Nine points.\NThat's equivalent of two lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.96,1:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me.\NTwo lifetimes earnings now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.00,1:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> $10. Yeah. $10 for a lifetime.\N>> Yeah, we went up 10 points. That's
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.04,1:14:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,really nice.
